were known only for $n\\leq18$ and odd $n\\leq21$ for the crossing number,\nand for $n\\leq14$ and odd $n\\leq21$ for halving lines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Feb 2011 19:02:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Mar 2011 15:14:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-19"}
