e of generalized\nzeros of the fixed balanced Hilbert-Burch matrix phi for a parameterization of\nC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Feb 2011 19:43:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Feb 2012 13:17:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-02-09"}
